  - extra-space-tolerant parsing: `test_etl.py:14`
  - end-to-end extraction/summarization: `test_etl.py:24`
  - exact report HTML structure: `test_etl.py:41`
  - environment-based configuration: `test_etl.py:57`
- Added a README documenting configuration and usage: `README.md:1`

